x1 = 10 
x2 = 32

length = 22

pixel_offset = 0
for (i = x1; i < x2; i++) {
	pixel_offset = 3 * i; 	-> 33
	scanline_ptr[pixel_offset] = blue;
	scanline_ptr[pixel_offset + 1] = green
	scanline_ptr[pixel_offset + 2] = red;
}


y = mx + b

=> b = y - mx

=> b = y1 - mx1

anti-aliased pixels become darker if on range [128, 255] 
anti-aliased pixels become lighter if on range [0, 127]

